data.meta_description:
111 likes, 0 comments - mytmgroup on October 17, 2023: "@litasuffian expresses her views on the future of TM's Customer Experience, emphasising that despite having a strong strategy in place, cultivating the appropriate organisational culture is paramount in achieving exceptional Customer Experience. 

At TM, we encourage our team to take initiative, show genuine concern, and exceed customer expectations in order to enhance our Customer Experience.

#TM #YourNextIsNow #LifeAtTM".
